Issue reporting complete

## Summary of Report Issue Feature

### Completed Implementation

1. **Issue Type Selector**
   - Dropdown with 6 issue types:
     - Missed Collection
     - Fly-tipping
     - Damaged Bin (NEW)
     - Overflowing Bin (NEW)
     - Street Lighting
     - Other Issue
   - Form validation with error messaging

2. **Description Text Field**
   - Multiline text input (4-6 lines)
   - Required field with validation
   - Inline error messages

3. **Photo Attachment (Camera/Gallery)**
   - Camera capture button
   - Gallery selection button (NEW)
   - Image preview thumbnail (NEW)
   - Remove photo option (NEW)
   - 5MB file size validation
   - Image compression (max 1920px, 85% quality)
   - Loading state during capture

4. **Location Picker (Optional Geolocation)**
   - Geolocator integration
   - Permission handling
   - Lat/Lng display after capture
   - Graceful fallback on denial

5. **Form Validation**
   - Issue type required
   - Description required
   - Optional postcode format validation
   - Clear inline error messages

6. **Submit with Confirmation Reference**
   - WN-prefixed reference numbers (e.g., WN12345678)
   - Loading state during submission
   - Error handling with retry

7. **Local Storage (Demo Mode)**
   - Reports saved to SharedPreferences
   - ReportRepository handles persistence
   - Reports survive app restart

8. **Success Confirmation Screen**
   - Animated transition to success card
   - Reference number prominently displayed
   - "Report another issue" button
   - "Back to home" button

### Files Modified
- lib/data/models/enums.dart (added damagedBin, overflowingBin types)
- lib/presentation/widgets/forms/photo_picker_button.dart (camera + gallery, preview, remove)
- lib/presentation/screens/report_issue/report_issue_screen.dart (section labels)

### Verification
- flutter analyze: No issues found
- flutter build web: Success
